17 SECTION 7. A new section to chapter 15-18.1 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
18 and enacted as follows:
19 Required national council for state authorization reciprocity agreements
20 membership.
21 A postsecondary educational institution offering distance education programs to students in
22 North Dakota must be a member of the national council for state authorization reciprocity
23 agreements and comply with the requirements of the council. Institutions must adhere to all
24 standards, policies, and fees established by the national council for state authorization
25 reciprocity agreements for membership and participation, including reporting requirements,
26 quality standards, and consumer protection measures.
